{"tid":110362,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Gmail 將不再支援於 XP 和 Vista 上的舊版本 Chrome 瀏覽器","createTime":"2017-02-06T15:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T09:12:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce9c9efd9b9cbaa03a91710a4e765889aef370e","tid":110362,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/6cd63bbe0c3df456e9f600390ef4366f/204898400/s.aolcdn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2F6cd63bbe0c3df456e9f600390ef4366f%2F204898400%2Fs.aolcdn.jpg&h=2d53d433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n儘管 Windows 10 的年度更新已經蓄勢待發，但坊間還是有不少人執意不升級其電腦的系統，除了微軟之外，現在就連 Google 也來督促這些人了。Google 宣布他們即將要推出包含重大安全性更新的 Chrome 55，屆時所有 Chrome 53 或以前版本的瀏覽器都會出現升級的提示。不過因為 Google 在 Chrome 49 之後就沒有再為 Windows XP 和 Vista 推出更新，所以這兩個系統的使用者也很合理地不獲升級。<br />\n<br />\n好了，要是不升級至最新版本 Chrome 瀏覽器的話，會怎樣呢？Google 指在 2017 年 12 月時，舊版本的 Chrome 瀏覽器就只能打開基本 HTML 版本的 Gmail，並且要承受諸多安全性風險。所以說，大家就別倔強，趕快從 XP 或 Vista 畢業了。"},{"pid":"31a0424aafe75e5ed7bbef0f254de006af4c341b","tid":110362,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:30:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22ffd3286faec66efd662e83fb1a44397614db14","tid":110362,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Vista呢舊垃圾真係會有人賴死唔升級咩...</blockquote><br />\nx p先係重點囉....................."},{"pid":"cb7a782b66869b16b0594a32cbe0de37c8193306","tid":110362,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"非常贊成，最好 win7 ;  8 ;  8.1都唔支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4034e96ba713d3e1dbc2c04ed72144ed5b3286d1","tid":110362,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:14:32.000Z","msg":"而家啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係一日唔減少downward compatibility,<br />\n一日都唔會有進步"},{"pid":"f213570d7be44af9f79dfd59dd354b79382d5653","tid":110362,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係一日唔減少downward compatibility,<br />\n一日都唔會有進步</blockquote><br />\n因為windows呃錢加垃圾囉,一個幾乎人人都用嘅系統居然賣七舊水咁貴??食水咁深??仲要每隔幾年升級一次??"},{"pid":"0d34c51aa165631f3700d68e24441348e2f36507","tid":110362,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係一日唔減少downward compatibility,<br />\n一日都唔會有進步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Backward compatibility</strong>我就聽過! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW, 呢個亦係Linus成日強調Linux應有既feature, 佢自己去maintain呢個OS時亦做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ; 可惜啲FOSS developers(尤其搞Desktop果啲)唔聽話, 一尾為改而改, 搞到每隔冇耐(通常唔駛半年)一upgrade就出現incompatibility既情況出現, 令就算veteran Linux users都無所適從! Linux Desktop搞得差, 唔注重backward compatibility, 絕對係造成Windows users唔想轉用Linux既一大主因! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWindows/Google越嚟越唔注重backward compatibility, 對users絕對係壞事嚟, 浪費晒地球有用既資源, 刻意製造無謂既垃圾, 我都no eye see了! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec1773830ac8276899604c7d5593681c94aa7d9","tid":110362,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:50:26.000Z","msg":"油頭毒撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c73722cb30ac24f17d94d69a0ae8f82d92a9025","tid":110362,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>油頭毒撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28Y8W.gif\" data-thumbnail-sr